file.name: editor.swagger.io.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  version: v1
  title: CWA-Data data donation API
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
paths:
  '/version/{version}/{mobile-os}/otp':
    post:
      summary: Post one-time-passcode (OTP)
      tags:
        - send otp
      parameters:
        - name: version
          in: path
          description: API version
          required: true
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/version'
        - name: mobile-os
          in: path
          description: Mobile operating system
          required: true
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/mobile-os'
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/x-protobuf:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/EDUSOneTimePasswordRequest'
            example: <BINARY DATA>
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OTP was valid and is now marked as used - it's redeemed
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                expirationDate:
                  value: |-
                    {
                      "expirationDate": "2021-02-16T08:34:00+00:00"
                    }
        '400':
          description: TBD
        '401':
          description: TBD
        '403':
          description: TBD
        '500':
          description: server errros while processing the request
  '/version/{version}/{mobile-os}/dat':
    post:
      summary: Data donation
      tags:
        - send data
      parameters:
        - name: version
          in: path
          description: API version
          required: true
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/version'
        - name: mobile-os
          in: path
          description: Mobile operating system
          required: true
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/mobile-os'
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PPADataRequest'
            example: <BINARY DATA>
      responses:
        '204':
          description: PPAC succeeded and the request was syntactically valid
        '400':
          description: TBD
        '401':
          description: TBD
        '403':
          description: TBD
        '500':
          description: server errros while processing the request
components:
  schemas:
    version:
      type: string
      description: 'A string of form ''v[\d+]'''
      example: v1
    mobile-os:
      type: string
      description: Either 'ios' or 'android'
      example: ios
    EDUSOneTimePasswordRequest:
      type: string
      format: binary
      description: TBD
    PPADataRequest:
      type: string
      format: binary
      description: TBD
